Short description of programs in this dirctory
-------------------------------------------------------------
extracthdr               extracts FITS parameter fields from
                         text files.
-------------------------------------------------------------
rfitshdr                 extracts FITS header fields directly
                         from the FITS files.
-------------------------------------------------------------
irafasc2asc              converts IRAF written text files to 
                         properly ordered text files.
-------------------------------------------------------------
convtim                  makes lists of UT and dates to time
                         file in seconds.
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.balmer                runs the Ix Balmer line-index software.
                         Now the new version (Nov.2000)!
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.old_balmer            the old Ix Balmer software.
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.hanspow               runs Hans' sine-wave fitting program 
                         to produce power spectrum.
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.makedata              makes artificial data/noise series.
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.clean                 finds amplitudes at given set of
                         frequencies iteratively.
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.extclean              makes files with the frequencies and
                         amplitudes from clean* files
-------------------------------------------------------------
ix.amplfunc              takes ampl* files and creates sorted
                         columns of mplitude for each frequency
-------------------------------------------------------------
findmean                 finds mean and scatter of a column
                         in a file
-------------------------------------------------------------
